The '''Gilt Gushers''' of [[Abregado-rae/Legends|Abregado-rae]] were a grouping of entirely natural fountain and [[Freshwater spring|spring]] formations located in the planets vast underdeveloped wilderness. They were named such, due to the fact that on rare occasions, flakes of pure [[Electrum/Legends|Electrum]] would bubble to the surface. It was not uncommon for prospectors to chase these occurrences so devotedly, often fruitlessly, that they went entirely insane.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

